⭐ DOCUMENT 6 — Public Announcement: Using the Badge Signals Intent
Title:
Using This Badge Signals Your Intent to Protect Your Work

Body:
By using the IP Continuity Watermark or the Repost Badge even once, you are signaling that you want your creative work 
to be protected through continuity and collective visibility. This badge represents participation in a global, creator‑driven 
effort to generate compounding protection by uniting and timestamping bodies of work across the world.

This system helps creators protect their work from absorption, mirroring, and unauthorized replication by establishing clear 
authorship and public notice.

This is a public‑safe layer of the VaultForge‑Live SAM‑VPS Continuity IP Protection System. No internal mechanics are exposed.
